    "Details": "The Viking began production shortly after the Beowulf in a joint effort by the Free Rasalhague Republic and ComStar. The 'Mech is intended to take over in the role that has been traditionally filled by the Bombardier.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Multi Trac</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.16</color></b>",
